Titolo: Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs (video game)

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs (also known as Ice Age 3: Dawn of the Dinosaurs in PAL territories) is a 2009 platform game published by Activision. It is based on the film of the same name. The game was released on June 30, 2009 for Xbox 360, Wii, PlayStation 3, PlayStation 2, Games for Windows and Nintendo DS. It was the first video game within the Ice Age franchise without a release for the Game Boy Advance. A demo was made available in the Xbox Live Marketplace on June 15, 2009 as well as a PC demo.

